These are Puzzles for 3x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-1::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: may, september, january, june, october, april, august
The people have 7 different jobs:  fisherman, designer, software-developer, architect, bartender, manager, security-guard
There 7 different types of food: mango, cherry, potato, grapes, pear, plum, garlic
 1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far left##1
 2. the person eating cherry is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 3. the person eating garlic is between the designer and the fisherman##2
 4. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person eating plum##1
 5. the designer is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in may is the person eating garlic##1
 7. the architect is between the person eating grapes and the person who's birthday is in october##2
 8. the person eating pear is on the left of the person eating plum##1
 9. the person eating plum is on the left of the person eating mango##1
10. the person who's birthday is in august is the software-developer##1
11. the manager is the person who's birthday is in june##1
12. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
13. the person eating mango is the bartender##1
14. the person who's birthday is in april is between the person eating potato and the person eating garlic##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |    7     |
| Birthday   | october | may     | april | september | june | august  | january  |
| Job   | fisherman  | architect        | designer  | security-guard     | manager   | software-developer       | bartender   |
| Food         | cherry   | garlic | grapes    | potato  | pear | plum | mango |

