.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-2::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: lemonade, iced-tea, water, juice, hot-chocolate, 7up, fanta
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: spy, epic, scientific, action, crime, satire, sports
The people have 7 different jobs:  security-guard, architect, entrepreneur, engineer, bartender, dressmaker, analyst
 1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the architect##1
 2. the person watching crime movies is the person watching crime movies##1
 3. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
 4. the person watching action movies is on the left of the security-guard##1
 5. the person watching spy movies is the person drinking fanta##1
 6. the person drinking lemonade is the engineer##1
 7. the person drinking lemonade is between the person watching sports movies and the analyst##2
 8. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 9. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
10. the person drinking water is on the right of the bartender##1
11. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
12. the security-guard is the person drinking iced-tea##1
13. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
14. the person drinking juice is on the right of the dressmaker##1
15. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1
16. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3       |    4     |   5    |     6     |    7     |
| Beverage   | 7up | fanta      | juice     | lemonade  | hot-chocolate | water | iced-tea |
| Movie-Genre         | epic  | spy | satire | scientific | sports | action   | crime  |
| Job     | entrepreneur   | dressmaker     | analyst        | engineer  | bartender   | architect       | security-guard      |

