 1. the person who's sport is handball is the havana-smoker##1
 2. the person who's sport is biathlon is the game-smoker##1
 3. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1
 4. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person playing snooker##1
 5. the person who's sport is skateboarding is between the person who's sport is badminton and the blend-smoker##2
 6. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 7. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
 8. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the blend-smoker##1
 9. the person who's sport is badminton is on the far right##1
10. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1
11. the person who's sport is handball is the havana-smoker##1
12. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
13. the person playing whist is on the left of the game-smoker##1
14. the person who's sport is badminton is the person playing backgammon##1
15. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1

.:: Answer ::.
