10. the person who likes orange is the person who's birthday is in august##1
11. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
12. the person who likes grey is between the person playing whist and the person playing domino##2
13. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person playing whist##1
14. the person who likes fuchsia is the person who's birthday is in december##1
15. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
