 3. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
 4. the fan disco is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
 5. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 6. the person playing domino is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
 7. the fan funk is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
 8. the owner of the rat is the person playing mah-jongg##1
 9. the person playing domino is between the owner of the cat and the owner of the hedgehog##2
10. the fan ambient is the owner of the rabbit##1
11. the fan folk is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
12. the person playing canasta is the fan reggae##1
13. the person playing poker is on the left of the fan ambient##1
14. the fan funk is on the right of the fan hip-hop##1

.:: Answer ::.
