There 7 different types of food: mango, orange, pear, apricot, kiwi, radish, watermelon
 1. the french is on the right of the indonesian##1
 2. the person eating radish is in the middle##1
 3. the italian is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
 4. the colombian is the person playing mah-jongg##1
 5. the person playing backgammon is on the far right##1
 6. the person eating radish is the indonesian##1
 7. the person eating pear is the person playing backgammon##1
