 9. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person eating orange##1
10. the person playing scrabble is in the middle##1
11. the chinese is on the right of the person eating orange##1
12. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person playing whist##1
13. the person eating apricot is on the left of the malaysian##1
14. the person playing billiard is between the person eating watermelon and the person playing monopoly##2
15. the person eating watermelon is the colombian##1

